/**
 * FastThriftServer integration test for code generated by `@cpp.FastServer`.
 *
 * Drives the full server-side pipeline (TransportHandler → MockHandler →
 * generated <Service>AppAdapter) end-to-end with a mocked transport, then
 * verifies request dispatch, declared/undeclared exception cascades,
 * unimplemented-method handling, and binary/compact protocol coverage.
 *
 * Companion microbenchmark: FastThriftServerIntegrationBench (added in a
 * separate diff).
 */

